ing: 1 (1.5 fluid ounce) jigger tequila (such as Jose CuervoÂ®)
1/2 fluid ounce coffee-flavored liqueur (such as Trader Vic'sÂ®)
des: "A mix of tequila and coffee liqueur that produces a unbelievable and not-too-sweet exotic drink. You will have to give this a try, even if you aren't fond of tequila!"
ins: Pour tequila and coffee-flavored liqueur into a shaker filled with ice; cover and shake until chilled. Strain drink into a martini glass. Garnish with a maraschino cherry.
